{"tid":1567243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［50000]連登仔同我一齊追債！","createTime":"2019-09-14T03:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T12:24:23.000Z","uid":20723,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1efd8b83fb13b5612214189168e885f6732354a0","tid":1567243,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAABnFb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAABnFb.png&h=5bd749e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caLar6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaLar6x.png&h=7febc0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">土支你今日還錢味啊？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=0da16733\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>記得Check verify email</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊係侵侵啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f